# Fallback - any unspecified files require maintainer review
* @maintainers

# =============================================================================
# TEAM DEFINITIONS (UPDATE THESE!)
# =============================================================================
# 
# Replace the following example team names with your actual GitHub teams/users:
#
# @frontend-team - Frontend developers responsible for HTML, CSS, JS
# @ui-ux-team - UI/UX designers responsible for visual consistency
# @backend-team - Backend developers working on Django
# @security-team - Security specialists
# @qa-team - Quality assurance engineers  
# @tech-writers - Technical documentation team
# @maintainers - Project maintainers and leads
# @devops-team - DevOps/Infrastructure team
#
# Example individual assignments:
# @john-doe - Lead developer
# @jane-smith - UI/UX lead
# @security-expert - Security specialist
#
# GitHub Teams format: @orgname/teamname
# Individual users format: @username
